metadata.name: XOLO Key Card
metadata.description: A key card given to all crew mates on one of the last shuttles departing from Earth. With this device, passengers are able to activate their beacon and be recognized in the ships database. Initiating the startup of this unique key card is irreversible. Once activated, your fellow ship members will be able to see your classified data entries and gear specifications. Use with the utmost diligence.
